OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The NHS will stop taking money from the
OL,6, gambling industry to treat people with 
OL,7, addiction, the NHS England national    
OL,8, mental health director has said.       
OL,10,FWriting to charity GambleAware, Claire 
OL,11,FMurdoch said the NHS would instead fund
OL,12,Fits own gambling services from 1 April.
OL,14,FThe gambling industry paid #16m to     
OL,15,FGambleAware between April and December 
OL,16,Fto help fund treatment services.       
OL,18,FOf this, #1.2m was awarded in grants to
OL,19,FNHS-run gambling clinics.              
